Bay gio toi se noi ro nhung viec ma toi can lam, GP Card la GlacierPeak Card, GP card hien dang locked, toi bay gio can unlock no, sau do toi se config de no co the boot pxe, sau do toi se vao console cua GP card de disable firewall, add public key ssh, va cuoi cung la export csr va token tu GP card ra. De lam duoc viec do, toi co 1 script python (unlock_gp.py) de tu dong hoa toan bo quy trinh do. Script se doc MAC address tu file, tim IP tu MAC, ssh vao Rack Manager, lay thong tin slot server, thay doi che do boot sang PXE, reset server, dang nhap vao console GP qua serial port, thuc hien cac cau lenh trong GP de disable firewall va add public key, va cuoi cung la xuat CSR va token ra. Neu co slot nao bi loi trong qua trinh thi se duoc ghi lai de sau nay xem lai. Sau day la code cua script unlock_gp.py ma toi da viet san sang su dung.

Sau khi generate ra duoc GP_CARD_SN thi trong thu vien /tmp/GP_CARD_SN se co 3 file: GP_CARD_SN.CSR, token.bin, va cert_0.der to cert_3.der. Thi bay gio toi script thu 2 (collect_csr_to_pxe.py) se duoc su dung de tu dong SCP thu vien /tmp/GP_CARD_SN tu GP card len may chu PXE, vao thu muc /home/qsitoan/April19_unlock/GP_CARD_SN. Script se doc MAC address tu file, tim IP tu MAC, lay thong tin slot server, dang nhap vao console GP qua serial port, kiem tra thu muc /tmp/GP_CARD_SN co ton tai hay khong, neu co thi se SCP to PXE, neu khong thi ghi lai loi. Cuoi cung se in ra ten thu muc chua cac file da duoc copy len PXE.
after we scp everything to our PXE at folder P20265082094308E. We will have like this:
